					<![CDATA[
						 <p>The giant penguin measurements are ~100x too big.</p> <p>The ocean is only ~3.5km deep on average. If an 80km long penguin dove in face first, only 5% of it's head will even get wet.</p> <p>Everest is only ~9km high.</p> 
				 	]]>
