				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13625473/scp-5271#post-4740640</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Fri, 07 Aug 2020 03:07:43 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>weizhong</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1777811</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>This is immensely silly, but damn it if it doesn't feel so like so much fun. On the surface, anomalous animal society <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-1845">has been</a> <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-2050">done quite</a> a bit, but the mental imagery of occult penguins summoning Penguin Jesus to come and kill all the seals was the bit that sealed the deal for me.</p> <p>One suggestion: MTF Vau-2 (&quot;Pingu&quot;) is&#8230;just a bit too on the nose for me. I think this would be improved if it were changed to something else, as it took me a bit out of the story.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
